casebody.data:
John T. CHISHOLM, et al., petitioners,
v.
TWO UNNAMED PETITIONERS, et al. No. 15-1416. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 3, 2016.

Motion of Center for Media and Democracy, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Wisconsin denied.
